，就是无法被公式化。","createdAt":"2025-07-31T18:22:22"},{"id":"0198602a-7895-70c9-bcad-6dbaf2eedce2","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":26138,"content":"人家发个帖子，也没恶意","createdAt":"2025-07-31T19:07:32"},{"id":"01986045-d567-7217-962b-c02b830f6f93","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3968,"content":"我就是单纯的发表一下自己的看法","createdAt":"2025-07-31T19:37:26"}]